Miranda wrote the music and lyrics for the musical In the Heights, which opened on Broadway at the Richard Rodgers Theatre in March 2008. Chapter 2 followed in 2021, Chapters 3 and 4 in 2025, and Chapter 5 slated for release in 2026, each accompanied by his music with minor contributions from other artists. In 2020, Fox contributed to the OMORI soundtrack.

Additionally, under the alias Radiation, Fox composed music for the webcomic Homestuck. https://www.last.fm/music/Toby+Fox
